title: Mujtaba Shuja Ur Rehman wins PP-148 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (PML-N) candidate, Mujtaba Shuja Ur Rehman has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-148, Lahore-IV by securing 37,998 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was independent candidate, Saba Dewan who bagged 31,560 votes.
The votersâ€™ turnout remained 36.25%.
